dominated by <PLACE continent="NA" form="NAM" gazref="igdb:840" id="P-54" state="us" type="COUNTRY">American</PLACE> and <PLACE continent="EU" country="GB" form="NAM" gazref="igdb:17389505" id="P-69" predicative="true" type="COUNTRY">British</PLACE> giants such as Exxon Mobil and BP.



